('953','The Devil in the Darkness <Epic>','43','70','1','0','0','0','0','1','0','952','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','443','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','443','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','94000','3000','35','254','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','You must defeat {c1}Astaroth{/c}, the King of Devils from another dimension, deep inside Aidion Neckria, then return to {c2}Integra Bloodmoon{/c}. {c1}Astaroth{/c} is a mighty fiend, far stronger than any one person, so it would be wise to recruit friends and allies to battle him together.','You''re a real hero, brother.From now on, you''ll be reborn as a Pagan of Darkness Heart.This will be a sign which will prove it. The hero who defeated Astaroth, the king of Devil of Another dimension~May Etain protect you!Now you''re a true hero in both word and deed. From this moment forth, your baptism as a Pagan of Darkness Heart is complete, and this shall be a sign to prove that you are the hero who defeated Astaroth, the King of Devils. May Etain protect you from harm.','','','May Mystra''s mighty power guard you from peril.','We can delay no longer. Now, you must venture deep into Aidion Neckria to the grave of Mornie, the progenitor of the Vail race. Astaroth, the King of Devils from another dimension, is planning to make that the site of his complete birth into this world, and you must put a stop to it. I''ve also been told that the "closed space" the Vail are using to seal off Aidion Neckria has reached its limit. If we delay any longer, our inner territories will become a war zone.Astaroth may well have some unknown power never before seen in this world, so even with the best preparation, there''s no guarantee you''re life is safe against his dark power. Make sure to go with a team you trust. Since the Vail and the Nordein are getting along better these days, I suppose it shouldn''t be too hard to find a group of allies. Go now, and come back safe.','May Mystra''s mighty power guard you from peril.','May Mystra''s mighty power guard you from peril.','964','1','0','0'), 
