s of Lapis, I''ll give you a Lapis that contains an unimaginable ability.If I asked you to collect more than that, it''s possible I wouldn''t see you again for a long time, but...well, if you''re feeling up to it, collect as many as you can.The monsters you''ll be looking for is ''Skulleron Big Ear Gnomes'' and ''Ellyuteion Plump Lizards'' that used to be raised for research.If I can ask for just one more thing, I hope you''ll come back with an empty bag when you return. The reward will be even better than you can imagine.','','Of course, obtaining a Lapis is probably your primary motive, but it''s even more important that we reduce the number of these monsters.','0','0','0','0'), 
