 your kind''s survival? Mortal! I have lost all my powers to the {c4}Cryptic One{/c}! You must restore the {c2}Power of King''s Wrath{/c} in order to bring me back to my true strength. Of course, it would take a long time. I need to recover as soon as possible, to keep Teos Epeiros... Mortal, I beseech you! Help me!','','This evil god will rise eternally unless I block  the dimensional tear. I was too hasty and caused this mess. It''s all my fault. ','0','0','0','0'), 
