('1933','Delicious Honey','60','62','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1731','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','272','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','272','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','317900','21265','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Bloody Grizzlys{/c} around the Temporary Post, and then report to {c2}Lenas Banntz {/c}.','Ha ha, now I can have a sip of this delicious honey!It''ll be like drinking a spoonful of gold! Honey is that expensive in the current market.','','','Those Grizzly bears may have sharp claws, but they''re merely unintelligent animals. ','Although water is very precious in this dry land of Valdemar Regnum, it''s still nowhere near as valuable as honey.I''m angry because those {c1}Bloody Grizzlys{/c} keep eating up so much of that precious nectar!Please go get rid of them so they won''t touch our honey.If they''re so desperate for water, they can drink Crowly or whatever else.','','Those Grizzly bears may have sharp claws, but they''re merely unintelligent animals. ','2511','200','0','0'), 
('1934','Special Ingredient','60','62','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1731','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','273','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','273','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','317900','21265','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Bloody Mad Boars{/c} at the Temporary Post, and then report to {c2}Grace Loen{/c}. ','Thank you. I hope that the remaining angelica shoots will bloom into beautiful flowers.Of course, that''s not possible unless you continue hunting those annoying boars.','','','I''m ready for some barbeque.','In Valdemar Regnum, it''s common to experience multiple battles with the enemy on a daily basis. That said, we''re short on almost every supply, especially angelica for making {c3}Healing Potions{/c}.To make matters worse, the {c1}Bloody Mad Boars{/c} have stomped and ruined the angelica shoots around the Temporary Post.If we lose this war because of a lack of healing potions, I''m going to hunt all those boars and host barbeque parties with their meat for every day of the year. That''s how spiteful I am.','','I''m ready for some barbeque.','2512','200','0','0'), 
('1935','Damaged Supplies','60','62','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1731','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','270','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','270','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','317900','21265','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Bloody Gray Wolves{/c} around the Temporary Post, and then report to {c2}Brent Paker{/c}. ','Thank you so much for subjugating those wolves.I''m sure the families of the rescue party members that were killed will also appreciate what you''ve done.By the way, those wolves are as hard to get rid of as weeds.Even though you hunted so many of them, it still seems that there are just as many as before...','','','I can''t sleep at night because of the roars of those wolves.','Our transport unit was raided by {c1}Bloody Gray Wolves{/c} near Valdemar while transporting supplies from Ereumana that were supposed to be used to build a new camp.We quickly dispatched a rescue party, but so many wolves raided them. Almost the entire party was killed. Our rescue party was able to retrieve some supplies, but they were too damaged to be of any use....I don''t know what to say to the families of the rescue party members that died. All I can do is avenge the deaths of their sons and daughters. ','','I can''t sleep at night because of the roars of those wolves.','2510','200','0','0'), 
('1936','Kelten''s Request','62','64','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1760','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','707','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','707','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','357637','23391','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Contaminated Human Warriors{/c} and 100 {c1}Contaminated Human Knights{/c} in the Dark Vine Land, and then report to {c2}Theodore Kelten{/c}.','I''m old, but I suppose I can still be of use.Time has made my ears and eyes go bad, but it couldn''t take away my gold!I''m glad that I have enough money to hire you again.','','','They were once like us, children of the Goddess.','{c2}Wendell{/c} is in charge of the defense of this Temporary Post, but the rest of us don''t just sit around and watch. Even our children are trying to help fight the enemy. That''s why being old and weak is no excuse! I can still help out somehow.Please defeat the {c1}Contaminated Human Warriors{/c} and the {c1}Contaminated Human Knights{/c} in the Dark Vine Land. I''ll pay you generously if you do.I may not be able to serve on active duty, but I''m wealthy enough to compensate for my weakness.','','They were once like us, children of the Goddess.','2514','100','2516','100'), 
('1937','Suffocating Land','62','64','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1760','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','699','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','699','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','357637','23391','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Contaminated Elf Mages{/c} and 100 {c1}Contaminated Human Priests{/c} in the Dark Vine Land, and then report to {c2}Bread Loen{/c}. ','Whew, now I feel better. It''s a little too early to relax: despite how you fought against them, the remaining Human Mages and Priests are still not afraid of using their black magic. ','','','What we''re doing is making a path for the light to shine through.','I feel like I''m suffocating from the ominous air coming from the Dark Vine Land.The {c1}Contaminated Elf Mages{/c} and the {c1}Contaminated Human Priests{/c} are polluting the air by exploiting their black magic. Everyone knows their minds are lost, but something needs to be done about their magic!Please go send the corrupt to hell so I can breathe fresh air again.','','What we''re doing is making a path for the light to shine through.','2515','100','2518','100'), 
('1938','Weapon of Light','62','64','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1760','0','0','0','0','0','1','3','45','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','3','45','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','357637','23391','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Contaminated Elf Rangers{/c} and 100 {c1}Contaminated Elf Archers{/c} in the Dark Vine Land, and then report to {c2}Marco{/c}.','We are killing two birds with one stone: killing the dangerous monsters in the Dark Vine Land and restocking weapons for our forces. Isn''t that great?','','','I''ll be looking forward to hearing some good news.','Don''t think that I don''t know anything about weapons simply because I''m an armor dealer.I don''t carry weapons myself, but I''m knowledgeable about high performance weapons that are available in the Light Confederation.By the way, did you know that those dangerous {c1}Contaminated Elf Rangers{/c} and {c1}Contaminated Elf Archers{/c} are still using our high quality weapons?Ludicrous, isn''t it? I thought about stealing their weapons, but then I''ve come up with a better idea: take the weapons but also get rid of their owners.What do you say? How''d you like to make my idea come true?  ','','I''ll be looking forward to hearing some good news.','2517','100','2519','100'), 
('1939','The Heart of the Enemy','62','64','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1760','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','271','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','271','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','357637','23391','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Contaminated Human Berserkers{/c} and 100 {c1}Contaminated Elf Wizards{/c} in the Dark Vine Land, and then report to {c2}Zenia Reeds{/c}.','Their hardened blood is spreading the dark energy of the Dark Vine Land everywhere else.None of them must be left alive.','','','Neo Girgo''s energy grants them even greater strength.','The Dark Vine Land is currently occupied by the {c1}Fallen Neo Girgo{/c}, which is disastrous for us.{c1}Neo Girgo{/c} forgot his duty as a member of the Light Confederation and has focused his efforts on annihilating us. His plan is going well, since he''s been assisted by soldiers like the {c1}Contaminated Human Berserkers{/c} and the {c1}Contaminated Elf Wizards{/c}. Please stop them from carrying out {c1}Neo Girgo{/c}''s plan.','','Neo Girgo''s energy grants them even greater strength.','2520','100','2521','100'), 
('1940','Obsession for Cobalt','61','63','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1743','1744','1745','0','0','0','1','8','134','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','8','134','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','317900','21265','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Nikelsaw Kobold Miners{/c} and 100 {c1}Nikelsaw Kobold Workers{/c} in the Nikelsaw Kobold Mine, and then report to {c2}Handel{/c}.','It wasn''t so difficult to take care of those Mini Chumps, was it?','','','I''m sorry, but I must stay and protect this post. ','I can never understand why the Nikelsaw Kobolds are so obsessed with cobalt.I know they''re not intelligent, but even so, cobalt doesn''t look that valuable to me.We Guards call the {c1}Nikelsaw Kobolds{/c}, Mini Chumps.Ha ha, don''t you think that name fits them perfectly?Of course, I''m not telling you this just to make you laugh.Please go defeat {c1}Nikelsaw Kobold Miners{/c} and {c1}Workers{/c} so they can never see their precious cobalt again.','','I''m sorry, but I must stay and protect this post. ','2523','100','2526','100'), 
('1941','Shelter in the Mine','61','63','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1743','1744','1745','0','0','0','1','7','698','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','698','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','317900','21265','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Nikelsaw Kobold Guards{/c} and 100 {c1}Nikelsaw Kobold Champions{/c} in the Nikelsaw Kobold Mine, and then report to {c2}Susanna York{/c}.','God, I can smell the stench of the Kobolds coming from you!Thank you, anyways. You''ve helped me get closer to my dream... Although we still have a lot of Kobolds to clear out of the mine.','','','My only concern about that place is its cleanliness since it''s been occupied by those stinky Kobolds.','Preparation leads to perfection.I''ve got a great plan! Are you interested in hearing it? As you know, this Temporary Post is as vulnerable as candlelight in the wind. If the monsters take over this place, we''ll have to wander this vast Valdemar Regnum without a home.I''m thinking about creating a secret shelter inside the Nikelsaw Kobold Mine.Even in the worst case scenario, we can use that shelter to rebuild this post again.Don''t you think it''s brilliant?Of course, we''ll have to clear out the {c1}Nikelsaw Kobold Guards{/c} and {c1}Nikelsaw Kobold Champions{/c} to secure that space for us.','','My only concern about that place is its cleanliness since it''s been occupied by those stinky Kobolds.','2524','100','2525','100'), 
('1942','Hell and High Water','61','63','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1743','1744','1745','0','0','0','1','7','697','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','697','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','317900','21265','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 170 {c1}Nikelsaw Kobold Soldiers{/c} and 30 {c1}Nikelsaw Kobold Chiefs{/c} in the Nikelsaw Kobold Mine, and then report to {c2}Benjamin Franklin{/c}. ','If I can make it back home after this war, it''ll be all because of you....Umm, speaking of which, do you think you could go and kill off more of them?','','','I''ll live to see the sun tomorrow, won''t I?','Life is difficult in general, but not many people have gone through hell and high water as I have... Well, at least that''s what I thought when I first arrived here.Have you seen the mine swarming with Kobolds?If they keep multiplying at this speed, we''ll soon be crushed or suffocated to death by them.I''m not ready to end my life that way, not yet. Please kill off as many {c1}Nikelsaw Kobold Soldiers{/c} and {c1}Chiefs{/c} as you can.','','I''ll live to see the sun tomorrow, won''t I?','2527','170','2528','30'), 
