('1946','Cheapskate Raciel','63','65','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1774','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','278','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','278','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','357637','23391','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}White Sand Lavas{/c} and 100 {c1}White Sand Pure Lavas{/c} at White Sand, and then report to {c2}Raciel Zimmerman{/c} in the Buried Camp. ','Hmm, you should know that I''m paying you more than you deserve.I usually don''t spend so much money on others, especially if they''re strangers.Of course, I''ll pay you even more if you keep taking care of those Lavas.','','','I think I can make some big money if I sell the poisonous stingers of those Lavas. ','What are you staring at? If you''ve got no items to buy or sell, then go away.Oh wait, you look strong enough to take care of the Lavas on White Sand for me.Young adventurer, how''d you like to work for me? If you take care of {c1}White Sand Lavas{/c} and {c1}Pure Lavas{/c}, I''ll pay you fairly for a job well done.','','I think I can make some big money if I sell the poisonous stingers of those Lavas. ','2546','100','2547','100'), 
('1947','In Dire Need of Vacation','63','65','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1774','0','0','0','0','0','1','3','47','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','3','47','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','357637','23391','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}White Sand Dust Lavas{/c} at White Sand, and then report to Blacksmith {c2}Bob Strayer{/c} in the Buried Camp. ','While you were fighting {c1}White Sand Dust Lavas{/c}, I repaired exactly 23 armors and 14 weapons.Please go back and take care of more of those Lavas. Otherwise, I''ll have to repair at least double that amount of equipment after just a little while!','','','Argh, I''m getting yet another batch of orders!','I don''t think those White Sand Lavas can live apart from their packs, even though each one is armed with a poisonous stinger. Did you know their sting is so poisonous that it can even kill a large Grizzly with just a prick?Thanks to them, my business couldn''t be better!They keep corroding weapons and armors, forcing our soldiers to bring me their equipment on almost a daily basis.But please get rid of those annoying {c1}White Sand Dust Lavas{/c}.I need at least one day off a month, just like everyone else. ','','Argh, I''m getting yet another batch of orders!','2548','200','0','0'), 
('1948','Scorpion Juice','63','65','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1774','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','718','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','718','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','357637','23391','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Crimson Scorpions{/c} and 100 {c1}Acid Scorpions{/c} at White Sand, and then report to {c2}Joanna Luis{/c} in the Buried Camp. ','It breaks my heart, but... I guess I should quit drinking scorpion juice.In fact, I''m kind of worried about the possible side effects to my health.I can''t make up my mind, knowing that so many scrumptious scorpions are still alive out there.Could you go back and take care of more of them?','','','Say, are those fresh and tasty scorpions still there? ','Some say that I have pretty disgusting taste, but that''s because they haven''t tasted crushed scorpion juice.If they keep criticizing my food choices, I might have to quit drinking that juice, but...I don''t think it''s possible as long as {c1}Crimson Scorpions{/c} and {c1}Acid Scorpions{/c} are alive in White Sand.','','Say, are those fresh and tasty scorpions still there? ','2549','100','2550','100'), 
('1949','Confident Philip ','63','65','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1774','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','717','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','717','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','357637','23391','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Freeze Scorpions{/c} at White Sand, and then report to {c2}Suspicious Philip{/c} in the Buried Camp. ','Ha ha, see? I told you that scorpions are nothing to be afraid of.How''d you like to keep hunting {c1}Freeze Scorpions{/c}?It''ll be great if you help me prove to the others that they''re just harmless beetles.','','','I''m going to tell you one more time: I''m never going to leave the safety of Arke, never!','I don''t understand why people are so afraid of scorpions.They''re just a different type of beetle with no flesh to enjoy.O-of course, I don''t have to hunt them to show others how brave I am......I''ve got enough money to hire someone like you to hunt {c1}Freeze Scorpions{/c} for me.','','I''m going to tell you one more time: I''m never going to leave the safety of Arke, never!','2551','200','0','0'), 
('1950','Explorer Berg','64','66','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1766','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','633','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','633','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','397375','25730','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Contaminated Sealakel Warriors{/c} in the Contaminated Oasis, and then report to {c2}Explorer Berg{/c} for a reward.','Ha ha, thank you for teaching them not to touch innocent Explorers like me.By the way, my travel bag still hasn''t turned up.While I''m looking for it, could you go back and defeat more Sealakels for me?','','','Some crazy monster aficionado once told me that monsters jump at you with their mouths open because they''re happy to see you. Can you believe that?  ','Today''s a perfect day for traveling, isn''t it?It''s punishment for Explorers like me to stay in one place, but I can''t leave here without my bag.Those damned {c1}Contaminated Sealakel Warriors{/c} ambushed me and stole my travel bag.Oh well, I''ve got no choice but to stay here and replace the soles on my shoes until my bag turns up from somewhere.Huh? Are you sure you want to get it back for me?I thank you for your kindness, but those Sealakels are pretty violent. On top of that, they''re even more dangerous since they''re infected by Crowly. Oh, I''m not saying that I don''t want your help. I just don''t want to see you get hurt, you know?','','Some crazy monster aficionado once told me that monsters jump at you with their mouths open because they''re happy to see you. Can you believe that?  ','2552','200','0','0'), 
('1951','Uncomfortable Request','64','66','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1766','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','281','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','281','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','397375','25730','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Contaminated Sealakels{/c} in the Contaminated Oasis, and then report to {c2}Earldrin McClung{/c} in Arke for a reward.','Thank you for your hard work, but it''s not enough to stop them from stealing our weapons.Please go back and hunt more of them.','','','I feel sorry for the {c1}Contaminated Sealakels{/c}, knowing that they''re going to be killed soon.','I personally have no problem with the Sealakels, but I understand that everyone else does since those creatures threaten their survival.I don''t like that they''re contaminating Arke''s oasis, our only water source, but it''s understandable since it''s their home.Despite the fact that they can''t be blamed, I must ask you to kill off the {c1}Contaminated Sealakels{/c}.They keep stealing from our transportation teams that bring in weapons from the capital city.I hope you understand that I really don''t like to do this, but we have no choice.','','I feel sorry for the {c1}Contaminated Sealakels{/c}, knowing that they''re going to be killed soon.','2612','200','0','0'), 
('1952','Suspicious Sealakels','64','66','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1766','0','0','0','0','0','1','6','36','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','6','36','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','397375','25730','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Contaminated Sealakel Shamans{/c} and 100 {c1}Contaminated Sealakel Champions{/c} in the Contaminated Oasis, and then report to {c2}Ciel Goldihen{/c} for a reward.','We don''t have to worry about their cunning shamans, at least for a while, but they will remain a problem as long as the Sealakels keep evolving.','','','They''ll definitely put up a strong resistance.','The {c1}Contaminated Sealakel Shamans{/c} are using wicked spells.They''re one of the oldest species that have existed here since the beginning of Teos. They''re as highly evolved as us, and are very cunning and calculating.Their shamans are... Phew, I''ve never seen anyone craftier.I''ll never feel safe if we just leave them alone. Please defeat them along with their escorts, the {c1}Contaminated Sealakel Champions{/c}.','','They''ll definitely put up a strong resistance.','2553','100','2554','100'), 
('1953','Defeating Golems','65','67','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1778','0','0','0','0','0','1','10','76','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','10','76','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','397375','25730','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Contaminated Golems{/c} at South Arke, and then report to {c2}Risen{/c} for a reward.','I hope they''ve been safely returned to the earth where they belong.This still isn''t the end: we must continue sending the golems back to the earth so they can rest in peace.','','','The ground shakes violently every time the golems take a step.','We spend our days seeking ways to strengthen and help our soldiers fight better for our Goddess.That''s our duty, to strive for everyone to be better off, not just ourselves.I also feel responsible for the Contaminated Golems that roam South Arke.They''re obviously a threat to the successful operation of the Light Confederation.If you defeat the {c1}Contaminated Golems{/c}, you would be working to ensure our bright future.','','The ground shakes violently every time the golems take a step.','2568','200','0','0'), 
('1954','Purifying the Fruits','65','67','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1778','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','636','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','636','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','397375','25730','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Urbus Helltooth Workers{/c} and 100 {c1}Urbus Helltooth Plunderers{/c} to the north of Urubs'' Advance Base, and then report to {c2}Summoner Alasse{/c} for a reward.','Why are there still so many workers and plunderers left?It''s not a bad idea if you bring and throw Crowly Fruits at the Furies, but our priority now is defeating the workers and plunderers.','','','They''re so big that you can only distinguish them by the color of their legs.','The sinful {c3}Crowly Fruits{/c} are cultivated in the Dilapidated Farmstead area.When the dark red berries fully ripen, {c1}Urbus Helltooth Workers{/c} and {c1}Plunderers{/c} harvest and supply them to the Urbus Queen.Let''s stop them before they deliver another batch of fruit to the Urbus Queen.Please go defeat {c1}Urbus Helltooth Workers{/c} and {c1}Plunderers{/c}.','','They''re so big that you can only distinguish them by the color of their legs.','2561','100','2564','100'), 
('1955','Alchemist''s Wish','65','67','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1778','0','0','0','0','0','1','10','77','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','10','77','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','397375','25730','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Urbus Helltooth Guards{/c} and 100 {c1}Urbus Helltooth Warriors{/c} located north of the Urbus'' Advance Base, and then report to {c2}Germander{/c} for a reward.','Whew, I can see so much farther without those giants blocking my sight.Many of them are still blocking the beautiful scenery with their gigantic moss-colored bodies. Would you go back and defeat more of them?','','','They''re bigger in person, aren''t they?','The Urbus Helltooths are really huge!I thought I''ve seen all sorts of monsters, but they''re the biggest I''ve ever seen.You see, we Elves are shorter than the Death Eaters, though we''re so much smarter.I want to see all those gigantic {c1}Urbus Helltooth Guards{/c} and {c1}Warriors{/c} lying flat on the ground and never getting up again. I want them cut down to size!','','They''re bigger in person, aren''t they?','2560','100','2562','100'), 
('1956','Displeased Eugene ','65','67','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1778','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','282','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','282','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','397375','25730','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Urbus Helltooth Gardeners{/c} and 100 {c1}Urbus Helltooth Berserkers{/c} in Urbus''s Advance Base, and then report to {c2}Eugene Clark{/c} in Arke Village for a reward.','I wouldn''t need to do this if those gardeners just stopped working and slept at night.You won''t stop taking care of them, will you? ','','','I hope I''m not asking you for too much.','Have you been to the Urbus Farm?It''s just a wasteland to me, but those muscle headed Helltooth slaves really treat it like a real farm. Well, they may be right considering how thickly {c3}Crowly Fruits{/c} grow over there.They''re so stupid that they don''t know how to grow {c3}Crowly Fruits{/c} quickly, which is fortunate for us. Their gardeners, however, are a potential threat.Since they''re born to be gardeners, they take care of the gardens and patches day and night, which leads to the Urbuses growing stronger.Please get rid of the {c1}Urbus Helltooth Gardeners{/c} along with the {c1}Urbus Helltooth Berserkers{/c}. We can''t let them continue their work!','','I hope I''m not asking you for too much.','2619','100','2563','100'), 
