('1962','Surviving in the New Land','66','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1782','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','275','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','275','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','437112','28303','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Crowly Cannibal Demons{/c} and 100 {c1}Crowly Murderers{/c} in the Dilapidated Farmstead area, and then report to {c2}Zacke{/c} in Ganeshi Village for a reward.','I''m impressed that you accomplished what Wingett had promised but didn''t actually do.I''ll have to see if you can keep taking care of the Crowly for us.','','','This barren Regnum was once a wide expanse of green grasslands.','I remember what that arrogant {c2}Diplomat Wingett{/c} promised.He told me he would exterminate the {c1}Crowly Cannibal Demons{/c} and the {c1}Crowly Murderers{/c} in the Dilapidated Farmstead area.Of course, he hasn''t kept that promise, and Humans and Elves like you have to pick up the slack. You don''t want to get kicked out of our village by those monsters, do you?','','This barren Regnum was once a wide expanse of green grasslands.','2580','100','2584','100'), 
