('1964','Ghost Whisper ','66','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1782','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','276','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','276','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','437112','28303','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Crowly Spirits{/c} in the Dilapidated Farmstead area, and then report to {c2}Nadal{/c} in Ganeshi Village for a reward.','I really hope I''ll never have to hear them again...','','','I can still hear them whispering in my ears.','When I''m alone at night, I can faintly hear them.I''m talking about the mean {c1}Crowly Spirits{/c} that are rumored to whisper and lure innocent people to their lair.I don''t want to become one of their victims!Brave warrior, please go send them to Gehenna where they belong.','','I can still hear them whispering in my ears.','2588','200','0','0'), 
('1965','Executing the Rebels','67','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1794','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','688','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','688','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','437112','28303','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Dark Fear Troll Berserkers{/c} in the Dark Fear Troll Camp, and then report to {c2}Guardian Bouyer{/c} in the Ganeshi Village.','You did a great job forcing the Trolls to accept their destiny.Of course, there are still more Trolls that need to be eliminated.','','','We Ganeshis won''t let anyone ruin our bright future.','We eat to live, but those dumb Trolls live to eat.Lately I''ve noticed that the {c1}Dark Fear Troll Berserkers{/c} are teaching their kind not to live to eat, but to eat to live.They''re rebels that cause us trouble by refusing their destiny.We don''t want them to become smarter! That''ll interfere with our plan to conquer their territory. I need your help to stop those rebellious Trolls.','','We Ganeshis won''t let anyone ruin our bright future.','2604','200','0','0'), 
('1966','Secret Elixir','67','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1794','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','689','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','689','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','437112','28303','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','As {c2}Fighter Bouyer{/c} asked, defeat 100 {c1}Cervuth Archers{/c} and 100 {c1}Cervuth Champions{/c} in the Servus Territory.','Ah, those agents of the skeletal mage must be irreversibly tainted with evil. Look at their wings: they''re too soft!Now, you must make a choice. Do you want to go back and bring me more useful wings? Or do you want to give up now?I understand if you want to give up. I wouldn''t want to see the slaves of that skeletal mage either.','','','... um, why are you staring at my wings?Don''t compare mine to the Servuses''. It''s an insult!','I saw you make some things to cure diseases, and I''m sorry that you don''t have the best remedy in the world: Servus wings.When you wrap that wing around a wound, it heals instantly! Ingesting the wing powder also cures internal diseases and bleeding.Go defeat the {c1}Cervuth Archers{/c} and the {c1}Cervuth Champions{/c}.We Ganeshis are generous enough to let you keep their wings for healing purposes.','','... um, why are you staring at my wings?Don''t compare mine to the Servuses''. It''s an insult!','2574','100','2575','100'), 
('1967','Cruel Decision','67','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1794','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','651','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','651','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','437112','28303','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','As {c2}Eldorame{/c} asked, defeat 100 {c1}Cervuth Workmen{/c} and 100 {c1}Cervuth Females{/c} in the Servus Territory.','We exhibit our greatest strength to protect our children. I know the egg guardians must have been very difficult to defeat.We''ll have to keep eliminating them as long as their queen doesn''t stop laying her eggs.','','','It''s their fate.','The Servus {c1}Queen Aidion{/c} lays her eggs with end.It''s so disgusting! What about the {c1}Cervuth Workmen{/c} and the {c1}Cervuth Females{/c}?They gladly spend their entire lives protecting her eggs.My head aches whenever I think about those eggs, our future enemies.Destroying every single egg is too much of a hassle, so I want you to defeat the workmen and the females.Without their guardians, those eggs have no chance of survival.','','It''s their fate.','2573','100','2578','100'), 
