('1971','Servant''s Duty','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1813','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','687','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','687','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Duiminas Zombie Warriors{/c} in the Duiminas Ruins, and then report to {c2}Tazio Andresen{/c}.','This stone definitely contains some incredible mana.It''s a shame that we''re easily captivated by evil instead of good.I respect you for being able to resist this stone''s compelling power.Would you be willing to go back and test your willpower against those stones again?','','','I suppose that''s what their karma brought them.','{c1}Desiree{/c}''s servant monsters have no choice but to listen to his commands because they''re controlled by the ancient ghost''s dark stone, which is enchanted with his evil magic.Many people succumbed to {c1}Desiree{/c} while trying to obtain those magic stones.In other words, they become his servants instead of stealing his power. {c1}Desiree{/c} also never allows his servants to run away.I think you''re different than the other adventurers. Do you think you can defeat the {c1}Duiminas Zombie Warriors{/c} without becoming {c1}Desiree{/c}''s servant?','','I suppose that''s what their karma brought them.','2599','200','0','0'), 
('1972','The Fallen','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1813','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','648','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','648','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Duiminas Zombie Wilds{/c} in the Duiminas Ruins, and then report to {c2}Ranger Eldora{/c} in the 2nd Army Corps Camp.','I sense their evil energy from you.Please cleanse your body and then come back....You want to go and fight them again, don''t you?','','','Did you get rid of the Duiminas Zombie Wilds?','The Duiminas Ruins are infested by the fallen {c1}Duiminas Zombie Wilds{/c}.They''re the old villagers that have turned into zombies by {c1}Desiree{/c}''s evil magic.The fallen {c1}Duiminas Zombie Wilds{/c} prey on innocent souls and use their energy to contaminate Valdemar Regnum.If we can cut down their numbers, even just a little bit, it''ll help us to reclaim the land of the Goddess.','','Did you get rid of the Duiminas Zombie Wilds?','2598','200','0','0'), 
('1973','Hunting Lavas','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1813','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','283','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','283','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Duiminas Dust Lavas{/c} and 100 {c1}Duiminas Tongs Lavas{/c} in the Duiminas Ruins, and then report to {c2}Rod Strol{/c} in the 2nd Army Corps Camp.','Wow, good job!I''m sure you did way better than everyone else playing the Lava hunting game.','','','I want to grow up quickly, so I can go hunt Lavas too.','Do you know the most popular game here in the 2nd Army Corps Camp?It''s Lava hunting!I want to play too, but I''m still too weak to even hold up a spear.I''ve noticed you''ve helped many people in this camp. You must be really strong, eh?Would you play the game for me?You''ll have tons of fun hunting {c1}Duiminas Dust Lavas{/c} and {c1}Duiminas Tongs Lavas{/c}!','','I want to grow up quickly, so I can go hunt Lavas too.','2596','100','2592','100'), 
('1974','Ruined Ancient Site','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1813','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','284','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','284','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Duiminas Poison Lavas{/c} in the Duiminas Ruins, and then report to {c2}William Wingett{/c} in the 2nd Army Corps Camp.','Thank you for your hard work.I hope you''ll keep exploring the ruins. There''s plenty of them around here.','','','I don''t feel like working, just like everyone else.','Most people in this camp are depressed after being influenced by {c1}Desiree{/c}''s evil energy.You can tell by their unwillingness to work or do anything.I''m trying to keep up my motivation, and I''m really glad to see someone as energetic as you.How''d you like to go explore the ruins for a change of pace?While you''re at it, I''ll appreciate if you can hunt the {c1}Duiminas Poison Lavas{/c}.','','I don''t feel like working, just like everyone else.','2591','200','0','0'), 
('1975','Once Upon a Time','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1813','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','709','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','709','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Duiminas Iron Tongs Lavas{/c} in the Duiminas Ruins, and then receive a reward from {c2}Sweetpea{/c} in the 2nd Army Corps Camp.','Thank you for helping me.But... Could you help me again? {c2}Lukivia{/c} changed her mind, saying that she wants me to go back and take care of more {c1}Tongs Lavas{/c}.It''s unfair, but I really really want to know her secret!','','','If I get to know her secret, I''ll be able to meet my Prince Charming!','I''m so jealous of the Gatekeeper {c2}Lukivia{/c}.She has such a beautiful face and glamorous figure!I asked her what her secret is, but she won''t tell me unless I go take care of the {c1}Duiminas Iron Tongs Lavas{/c} in the Duiminas Ruins.{c5}Sweetpea is looking at you with irresistible puppy dog eyes.{/c}You''ll help me, won''t you?','','If I get to know her secret, I''ll be able to meet my Prince Charming!','2593','200','0','0'), 
('1976','Avenge My Daughter','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1813','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','285','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','285','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','251','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Duiminas Zombie Wilds{/c} in the Duiminas Ruins, and then receive a reward from {c2}Babiana Maea{/c} in the 2nd Army Corps Camp.','I hope my daughter Minerva can rest in peace now.','','','You can never forgive yourself for letting your children pass away before you do.','I don''t know if I''ll live to feel joy again.They took away my daughter Minerva. She meant everything to me.Please avenge my daughter by destroying the {c1}Duiminas Zombie Wilds{/c} in the blackened, evil land. I want all of them are punished. ','','You can never forgive yourself for letting your children pass away before you do.','2598','200','0','0'), 
