('2006','Guardian Creature''s Rebirth','65','67','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1880','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','604','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','604','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','397375','25730','25','252','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Atrocious Fog Antelopes{/c} and 100 {c1}Frosthorn Black Oxes{/c} at North Abarona, and then receive a reward from {c2}Stranger Leca{/c}.','I''m sorry, but this won''t be enough.Please try harder until this land is clear of all those contaminated animals.','','','Did you take care of the contaminated animals?','Since ancient times, our family has been travelling to find the holy Guardian Creature of the ancient god Asmodeus.Believing in the legend that the creature will be reborn in Palaion Regnum, my father, who also was the former leader of our family, ordered me to come here and wait for its rebirth.That creature, however, cannot be reborn now because the energy of the local animals has been tainted by the Crowly-contaminated land.Please exterminate the {c1}Atrocious Fog Antelopes{/c} and the {c1}Frosthorn Black Oxes{/c} and help me make that creature''s rebirth possible. ','','Did you take care of the contaminated animals?','2689','100','2690','100'), 
('2007','Energy of the Land','65','67','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1880','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','261','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','261','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','397375','25730','25','252','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 140 {c1}Steelhorn Cannibal Gaurs{/c} and 60 {c1}Violent Fanhorn Antelopes{/c} at North Abarona, and then receive a reward from {c2}Habita{/c}.','Some may think this isn''t important, but this must be done to ensure the safety of us all.','','','Were you able to relieve the land''s suffering?','I''ve sensed an unsettling energy in the land.Perhaps the land is angry at the {c1}Steelhorn Cannibal Gaurs{/c} and the {c1}Violent Fanhorn Antelopes{/c} for digging up the soil and drying up all the plants.It''s time for us to intervene and stop them from inflicting more pain to the precious land of the Goddess.','','Were you able to relieve the land''s suffering?','2687','140','2688','60'), 
('2008','Successor of the Family (2)','65','67','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1880','0','0','0','0','0','1','3','43','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','3','43','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','397375','25730','25','252','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Palaion Goblin Soldiers{/c} and 100 {c1}Palaion Goblin Assassins{/c} at East Abarona, and then receive a reward from {c2}Barsha Derkan{/c} in Abarona.','Thank you, but I don''t think this will be enough to improve my reputation and ensure my place as leader of our family.Help me again, and then I''ll reward you greatly as soon as I inherit the title as leader of our family from my father.','','','I don''t know who my father is going to choose as the next leader of our family.','We Derkans have been blacksmiths for generations.My youngest brother Wusha isn''t interested in the family business, but my other two brothers and I are all rivals for the position as the next leader of the family.I''ve heard that Hasha was distinguished for his service at the Bladewind Post.Nonetheless, I am the best at forging among the four of us. It''s only natural for me to be the next leader of our family.Please defeat the {c1}Palaion Goblin Soldiers{/c} and the {c1}Palaion Goblin Assassins{/c}, and let everyone else know that I''m the one that is meant to lead my family.','','I don''t know who my father is going to choose as the next leader of our family.','2698','100','2697','100'), 
