('2018','Delivering Combat Supplies','67','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1898','0','0','0','0','0','1','8','146','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','8','146','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','437112','28303','25','252','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Arised Peasantrys{/c} in the Dilapidated Farmstead area, and then receive a reward from {c2}Zidden{/c} in Abarona.','I knew you would be able to do it.Perhaps helping commoners like me is more honorable than serving on active duty.What do you say? Would you help me for the honor of our alliance?','','','First, we need to secure more weapon materials.','It''s common to see multiple engagements in Palaion Regnum on a daily basis.Thanks to the soldiers, every weaponsmith in the region is ordering a high amount of metal, but there''s no way that my supply can meet such a great demand.Then, I thought about the deserted farming equipment in the Dilapidated Farmstead area. They''re rusty and broken, but they still have the metal I need.Would you please go get rid of the {c1}Arised Peasantrys{/c} and bring me their equipment?  ','','First, we need to secure more weapon materials.','2715','200','0','0'), 
('2019','Surprise Attack','67','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1898','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','683','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','683','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','437112','28303','25','252','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Hungry Poison Pus Corpses{/c} in the Dilapidated Farmstead area, and then receive a reward from {c2}Chef Joubert{/c} in Abarona.','Thanks, but there are still so many more monsters to be exterminated.','','','Don''t blame me if you get hurt in battle, though.','There is a right time for everything.Now is our time to attack the {c1}Hungry Poison Pus Corpses{/c} in the Dilapidated Farmstead area: they''ve just been resurrected by black magic and are still not familiar with their surroundings.Why don''t you attack them by surprise?I''m sure this deed will help you earn some great recognition.','','Don''t blame me if you get hurt in battle, though.','2717','200','0','0'), 
('2020','Selene''s Problem ','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1917','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','622','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','622','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','252','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Lost Wolf Wraiths{/c} and 100 {c1}Laboratory Doorkeeper Gargoyles{/c} in front of Tanuvie''s Lab, and then receive a reward from {c2}Selene Wheaten{/c} in Abarona.','{c5}Thick black smoke rises as soon as Selene throws a Black Smoke Fruit at the ground.{/c}Ha ha, you see? This fruit will scare anyone!Wait, I don''t think these {c3}Black Smoke Fruits{/c} would be enough to surprise everyone I know. Could you bring me more?','','','I''ll meet with you soon, so I can pick up those Black Smoke Fruits.','It was worth convincing {c2}Lampen{/c} to let me come to this base. I love it here!I''ve got so many things to tell my friends when I get back home.Speaking of which, do you think they''ll believe me? What if they think I''m lying?Well, I guess it won''t be a problem. If they make fun of me, I''ll scare them by throwing Black Smoke Fruits. Here''s the problem: the fruits are available from the {c1}Lost Wolf Wraiths{/c} and the {c1}Laboratory Doorkeeper Gargoyles{/c} in front of Tanuvie''s Lab, but I''m too weak to fight them. I can try to pick up a few on the ground, but they''ll probably kill me before I can get any.   ...You''ll take care of them for me, won''t you?  ','','I''ll meet with you soon, so I can pick up those Black Smoke Fruits.','2750','100','2720','100'), 
('2021','Deathly Farewell','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1917','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','620','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','620','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','252','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Failed Mutative Chimeras{/c} in Tanuvie''s Lab, and then receive a reward from {c2}Oracle Endymion{/c} at the Expeditionary Base.','Did they accept their deaths?This isn''t over quite yet.We still have many souls that must be expelled from the realm of the living.','','','Did you take care of the {c1}Failed Mutative Chimeras{/c}?','When the Goddess''s wrath fell upon this laboratory, most of the mutant chimeras of the ancient Duiminases were killed.When their ancient ruins recently resurfaced, the ghosts of the {c1}Failed Mutative Chimeras{/c} appeared, roaming inside the lab as if they didn''t know they were dead.The dead and living cannot coexist like this. Please send those ghosts back to where they belong.','','Did you take care of the {c1}Failed Mutative Chimeras{/c}?','2722','200','0','0'), 
('2022','The Disgusting Mutatings','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1917','0','0','0','0','0','1','1','266','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','1','266','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','252','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Mutatings{/c} in Tanuvie''s Lab, and then receive a reward from {c2}Miriam Palaci{/c} in the Expeditionary Base.','You did the right thing: exterminating those disgusting creatures should have been our top priority!','','','It gives me the chills to just look at them, even from a safe distance!','Have you seen the disgusting-looking {c1}Mutatings{/c}?They''re in front of Tanivie''s Lab, squirming their grotesque protrusions that look like feelers or tongues.Gosh, what is {c2}Max{/c} thinking?  To me, those Mutatings are more threatening than Queen Caput!Oh, are you getting ready to exterminate {c1}Mutatings{/c}? Thank you so much for agreeing to do this!','','It gives me the chills to just look at them, even from a safe distance!','2721','200','0','0'), 
