('2028','His Ambition','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1917','0','0','0','0','0','1','8','143','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','8','143','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','252','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 100 {c1}Caput Slave Helltooths{/c} and 100 {c1}Caput Slave Hunters{/c} in the Caput Advance Base, and then receive a reward from {c2}Patrol Rackenin{/c} in the Expeditionary Base.','This still isn''t enough: the Caput army in the base camp is much larger than what you can imagine.','','','I suppose Max is a fairly admirable man, but I''ve seen others that have proven to be even more capable.','If I become a commander, I can march straight to the Caput Queen and finish {c1}Queen Kaizerin{/c} more quickly than Max can.You don''t believe me, do you?For your information, I made Max realize that subjugating the {c1}Caput Slave Helltooths{/c} and the {c1}Caput Slave Hunters{/c} is the only way to quickly conquer the Caput Advance Base.If you still don''t believe me, go hunt them. You''ll see that I was right.If you do that, I just might hire you as my aide when I replace Max.','','I suppose Max is a fairly admirable man, but I''ve seen others that have proven to be even more capable.','2733','100','2734','100'), 
('2029','Proving Her Strength','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1917','0','0','0','0','0','1','10','74','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','10','74','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','252','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Deadly Poison Huge Larvas{/c} at Northwest Abarona, and then receive a reward from {c2}Arien{/c} in Abarona.','Ho ho, I can''t wait to see Slav''s angry face!Of course, this isn''t enough to make him really mad. No, not just yet.','','','Enough is enough! I''m sick of him looking down on me.','{c2}Slav{/c} is my old nemesis.When I started this job, I thought that I wouldn''t have to see him again.It just so happens that I''ve met him again here in Palaion Regnum.I hate him for underestimating me because I''m a woman! I''d love to knock the stuffing out of him, but I''d rather prove him wrong! The {c1}Deadly Poison Huge Larvas{/c} in the Dilapidated Farmstead area seem to be the perfect target for showing him my strength.Could you help me?','','Enough is enough! I''m sick of him looking down on me.','2692','200','0','0'), 
