('2031','Eliminating Obstacles','68','68','1','1','1','1','1','1','1','1917','0','0','0','0','0','1','7','609','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','2','7','609','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','476850','31133','25','252','1','0','0','1','0','0','1','0','0','Defeat 200 {c1}Predator Blood Spiders{/c} at North Abarona, and then receive a reward from {c2}Alchemist Visto{/c} in Abarona.','Thank you so much! I can tell that the air is much cleaner and purer now.It''s still not clean enough to preserve the test results, though.Would you go back and hunt more {c1}Predator Blood Spiders{/c}?','','','I have to do everything I can so I don''t fail my master.','I''m here under the order of my master Thillue, who wishes to continue his Purification Crystal research here in Abarona. My duty is to produce the final test results with a completed version of the Purification Crystal.My work is going nowhere because those {c1}Predator Blood Spiders{/c} breathe poison that keeps ruining the test results.My master is usually a generous man, but he can be very angry when someone interrupts his studies. Besides, I don''t want to disappoint him.If you don''t mind, would you get rid of the {c1}Predator Blood Spiders{/c} for me? ','','I have to do everything I can so I don''t fail my master.','2694','200','0','0'), 
